\frametitle{Observations}
\begin{itemize}
\item \verb|\shadowbox{}| is from the package
\texttt{fancybox}. There are tons of similar useful and less useful packages
available at the Comprehensive TeX Archive Network (CTAN).
\item To define new high level logical commands, one of course needs to know
something about the low level \LaTeX{} ``programming''.
\end{itemize}
